verse.name: v1
verse.lines: {lang-eng}Who is like unto You Oh Lord, among gods? Who is like unto You, Glorious in holiness Fearful in praises Doing wonders ….. Who is like unto You?{/lang-eng}

verse.name: v2
verse.lines: {lang-eng}There is no one like You Oh Lord, among gods. There is no one like You, Glorious in holiness Fearful in praises Doing wonders …… There is no one like You!{/lang-eng}

verse.name: v3
verse.lines: {lang-eng}You’re my wisdom, oh Lord And You are my goal. You are the strength of my heart And in You I am whole. You are my vision and song And to You I belong …. There is no one like You!{/lang-eng}
